<h2>Rules for Manual Edits</h2>
<p>If you edit files directly instead of using the CLI:</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Read <code>CONVENTIONS.md</code> first</strong></li>
<li><strong>Include complete frontmatter</strong> in new notes</li>
<li><strong>Update <code>updated</code> field</strong> when modifying</li>
<li><strong>Update indices</strong>: <code>_tags.md</code>, <code>_graph.md</code>, directory <code>_index.md</code></li>
<li><strong>Build bidirectional links</strong> via the <code>related</code> field</li>
<li><strong>File names</strong>: lowercase with hyphens</li>
<li><strong>Internal links</strong>: <code><a href="filename.html">filename</a></code> (no <code>.md</code> extension)</li>
</ol>
<h2>Environment Variables</h2>
<ul>
<li><code>OA_VAULT</code> — Vault path (so you don't need <code>--vault</code> every time)</li>
<li><code>OA_TIMEZONE</code> — Timezone for dates (default: UTC)</li>
<li><code>OA_NO_OFFICIAL_CLI</code> — Disable Obsidian CLI bridge (set to 1)</li>
<li><code>OA_OPENAI_KEY</code> — OpenAI API key for embedding search</li>
</ul>
